# Bike Race Stem Planner

A professional tool for cycling teams to create race stem cards with route information.

## For Cyclists and Team Members

**Using the App:**
1. Visit [https://username.github.io/bike-race-stem-planner](https://username.github.io/bike-race-stem-planner)
2. Follow the on-screen instructions to create your race plan
3. Save your plan to your device using the "Export to File" button
4. Share the plan with teammates who can import it using the "Import from File" button

