## For Developers

This project uses:
- React (via CDN)
- Lucide icons
- Tailwind CSS (via CDN)

To run locally:
1. Clone the repository
2. Open index.html in your browser

To deploy changes:
1. Make your changes
2. Commit and push to GitHub
3. GitHub Actions will automatically deploy to GitHub Pages